      <title>七国集团领导人与教皇方济各合影留念</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/g-7-leaders-gather-for-historic-family-photo-with-pope-francis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[没有什么比七国集团的全家福更能体现世界领导人的心情了。他们认为受到轻视而怒不可遏，不受欢迎的领导人被排挤到幕后，脸上露出的笑容似乎有点勉强，因为国内还有这么多问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/g-7-leaders-gather-for-historic-family-photo-with-pope-francis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特财富基金进军拉丁美洲 吸引里约亿万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/saudis-woo-billionaires-in-rio-as-wealth-fund-taps-latin-america</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯王国在“投资尊严”的口号下，在巴西最著名的海滩举办了为期三天的峰会，向世界表明它已准备好在拉丁美洲开展业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/saudis-woo-billionaires-in-rio-as-wealth-fund-taps-latin-america</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日尔因边界纠纷禁止中国通过贝宁出口石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/niger-stops-chinese-oil-exports-through-benin-over-border-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日尔关闭了一条通过邻国贝宁港口出口原油的输油管道，这加剧了两国在边境僵局持续情况下的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/niger-stops-chinese-oil-exports-through-benin-over-border-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:27:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制裁以色列极端组织，因其破坏加沙援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/us-sanctions-israeli-extremist-group-tzav-9-for-destroying-gaza-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院对一个以色列极端组织实施制裁，该组织被指控阻挠和破坏对加沙地带巴勒斯坦人的援助，这是美国为缓解联合国所说的加沙地带迫在眉睫的饥荒而采取的最新措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/us-sanctions-israeli-extremist-group-tzav-9-for-destroying-gaza-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟选举惨败后，舒尔茨被要求加强领导力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/scholz-pressed-to-sharpen-his-leadership-after-eu-election-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲选举惨败之后，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的政党正不断向德国领导人施压，要求其展现更积极的领导力，首先是就 2025 年联邦预算与执政联盟展开争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/scholz-pressed-to-sharpen-his-leadership-after-eu-election-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:03:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>祖马在支持他的南非省份中被击败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-africa-s-kwazulu-natal-elects-ifp-s-ntuli-as-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非夸祖鲁-纳塔尔省议员选举因卡塔自由党官员担任省长，这对前总统雅各布·祖马所领导的在该地区赢得最多选票的因卡塔自由党造成了沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-africa-s-kwazulu-natal-elects-ifp-s-ntuli-as-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:58:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚的目标是实现 2020 年疫情以来最大的财政赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/colombia-targets-widest-fiscal-deficit-since-2020-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于税收收入下降导致国家财政出现缺口，哥伦比亚即将出现自新冠疫情以来最严重的财政赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/colombia-targets-widest-fiscal-deficit-since-2020-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:49:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
